H) Device statistics

  • Percentage of MEMORY and STORAGE usage during the crash.

1) Analysis for Samsung

1.1) Correlation Coefficient for samsung and important variables

1.1.1) Correlation between Samsung and Java class problems

* Sam.crash : Events for samsung * ConfirmPush, RealCall, Cookie and Realinter are java class problems that brought the event.

1.1.2) Correlation between Samsung and Memory usage over time

  • Sam.crash : Events for samsung
  • mem_less33 : 33% and less of Memory usage during the event
  • mem_between : 34% - 65% of Memory usage during the event
  • mem_grt66 : 66% and higher of Memory usage during the event

1.1.3) Correlation between Samsung and Storage usage over time

  • Sam.crash : Events for samsung
  • stor_less33 : 33% and less of Story usage during the event
  • stor_between : 34% - 65% of Story usage during the event
  • stor_grt66 : 66% and higher of Story usage during the event

1.1.4) Correlation between Samsung and frame_file

* Sam.crash : Events for samsung * frame1 : LoginContentProvider.java * frame2 : ConfirmPushNavFragment.java * frame3 : Parcel.java * frame4 : PfmData.java * frame1-4 : they are top four frame_file problems that contributed for the events.

2) Analysis for HUAWEI
